SELECT 
        sales_fact.Sales_channel,
        sales_fact.procured_date,
        sales_fact.order_date,
        sales_fact.ship_date,
        sales_fact.delivery_date,
        sales_fact.team_id,
        sales_fact.customer_id,
        sales_fact.store_id,
        sales_fact.product_id,
        sales_fact.order_quantity,
        sales_fact.discount_applied,
        sales_fact.unit_price,
        sales_fact.unit_cost,
        customers.customer_names,
        products.product_name,
        store_location.state,
        sales_team.team_names
FROM PORT_PROJECT.ANALYTICS.stg_sales_fact sales_fact
JOIN PORT_PROJECT.ANALYTICS.dim_customers AS customers ON sales_fact.customer_id = customers.customer_id
JOIN PORT_PROJECT.ANALYTICS.dim_products AS products ON sales_fact.product_id = products.product_id
JOIN PORT_PROJECT.ANALYTICS.dim_sales_team AS sales_team ON sales_fact.team_id = sales_team.team_id
JOIN PORT_PROJECT.ANALYTICS.dim_store_location AS store_location ON sales_fact.store_id = store_location.store_id

WITH Average_delivery_days AS (
 SELECT 
        AVG(DATEDIFF(DAY, Order_Date, Delivery_Date)) AS Average_delivery_days
    FROM 
         PORT_PROJECT.ANALYTICS.fct_sales
)
SELECT *
FROM Average_delivery_days

WITH Average_delivery_days AS (
 SELECT 
        AVG(DATEDIFF(DAY, Order_Date, Ship_Date)) AS Average_shipping_days
    FROM 
         PORT_PROJECT.ANALYTICS.fct_sales
)
SELECT *
FROM Average_delivery_days

WITH Profit_per_Customer AS (
 SELECT 
        customers.Customer_Names,
        ROUND(SUM((Unit_Price - Unit_Cost) * Order_Quantity * (1 - Discount_Applied)), 0) AS Profit_per_customer
    FROM 
        PORT_PROJECT.ANALYTICS.fct_sales sales_fact
    LEFT JOIN 
       PORT_PROJECT.ANALYTICS.dim_products AS products ON products.product_id = sales_fact.product_id
    LEFT JOIN 
        PORT_PROJECT.ANALYTICS.dim_customers AS customers ON customers.customer_id = sales_fact.customer_id
    LEFT JOIN 
        PORT_PROJECT.ANALYTICS.dim_store_location AS store_location ON store_location.store_id = sales_fact.store_id
    GROUP BY 
        customers.Customer_Names
    ORDER BY 
        Profit_per_customer DESC
)
SELECT *
FROM Profit_per_Customer

WITH Revenue_Per_State AS (
 SELECT 
        store_location.state,
        ROUND(SUM((Unit_Price * Order_Quantity) * (1 - Discount_Applied)), 0) AS Revenue_Per_State
    FROM 
      PORT_PROJECT.ANALYTICS.fct_sales AS sales_fact
    LEFT JOIN 
      PORT_PROJECT.ANALYTICS.dim_products AS products ON products.product_id = sales_fact.product_id
    LEFT JOIN 
        PORT_PROJECT.ANALYTICS.dim_customers AS customers ON customers.customer_id = sales_fact.customer_id
    LEFT JOIN 
        PORT_PROJECT.ANALYTICS.dim_store_location AS store_location ON store_location.store_id = sales_fact.store_id
    GROUP BY 
        store_location.state
    ORDER BY 
        Revenue_Per_State DESC
)
SELECT *
FROM Revenue_Per_State

WITH Total_Product_Revenue AS (
 SELECT 
        products.product_name,
        products.product_id,
        ROUND(SUM((Unit_Price * Order_Quantity) * (1 - Discount_Applied)), 0) AS Total_Product_Revenue
    FROM 
         PORT_PROJECT.ANALYTICS.fct_sales sales_fact
    LEFT JOIN 
         PORT_PROJECT.ANALYTICS.dim_products  AS products ON products.product_id = sales_fact.product_id
    LEFT JOIN 
       PORT_PROJECT.ANALYTICS.dim_sales_team AS sales_team ON sales_team.team_id = sales_fact.team_id
    LEFT JOIN 
         PORT_PROJECT.ANALYTICS.dim_store_location AS store_location ON store_location.store_id = sales_fact.store_id
    GROUP BY 
        products.product_name, products.product_id
    ORDER BY 
        Total_Product_Revenue DESC
)
SELECT *
FROM Total_Product_Revenue
